{"id":2900,"date":"2025-06-05T13:39:48","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:39:48","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2900"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:20:41","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:20:41","slug":"cap-am-cho-da-dau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/cap-am-cho-da-dau\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u &#8211; B\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00fang hay sai nh\u1ec9? Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng<\/span><\/i><b><i> c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ea7u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t! V\u1eady l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eddn r\u00edt, b\u00edt t\u1eafc? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay b\u00ed quy\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-dau-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Da d\u1ea7u l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5: Da d\u1ea7u l\u00e0 g\u00ec? L\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng b\u1edfi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, khi\u1ebfn da th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u00f3ng nh\u1eddn, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T (tr\u00e1n, m\u0169i, c\u1eb1m) v\u00e0 hai b\u00ean m\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da d\u1ea7u:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 l\u1edbp d\u1ea7u b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi m\u1edbi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00edt k\u00edn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da c\u00f3 v\u1ebb d\u00e0y h\u01a1n c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2904\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2904\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/cap-am-cho-da-dau\/da-dau-la-gi\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2904\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2904\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-dau-la-gi.webp\" alt=\"Da d\u1ea7u l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-dau-la-gi.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-dau-la-gi-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-dau-la-gi-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-dau-la-gi-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2904\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da d\u1ea7u l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu do:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc: Da g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u1ea9m, tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m: Khi da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng: G\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eady th\u00ec, tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef3 kinh ho\u1eb7c khi tinh th\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng da d\u1ea7u c\u0169ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u00e0 l\u00e0n da n\u00e0y l\u00e3o h\u00f3a ch\u1eadm h\u01a1n nh\u1edd l\u1edbp d\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-can-duong-am-cho-da-dau\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Khi thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m, da c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ti\u1ebft th\u00eam d\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2905\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2905\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/cap-am-cho-da-dau\/duong-am-da-dau\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2905\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2905\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/duong-am-da-dau.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/duong-am-da-dau.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/duong-am-da-dau-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/duong-am-da-dau-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/duong-am-da-dau-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2905\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"han-che-tiet-dau-qua-muc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi da \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea9m, tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u1ea1ng gel, lotion ho\u1eb7c serum c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, d\u1ec5 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u. Gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ngan-ngua-lao-hoa\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9 da d\u1ea7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a ch\u1eadm h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m, da v\u1eabn nhanh ch\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng serum c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ch\u1eadm l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giam-ngua-ngay-tho-rap\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y, th\u00f4 r\u00e1p<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e0ng d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ki\u1ec1m d\u1ea7u m\u1ea1nh th\u00ec da c\u00e0ng s\u1ea1ch. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, d\u1ec5 bong tr\u00f3c v\u00e0 g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y. D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ea7u \u2013 n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean da, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n ch\u1ee9a retinoids hay acid salicylic, da r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb kh\u00f4. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u1edbp khi\u00ean ch\u1eafn, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t v\u00e0 bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"top-cac-thanh-phan-cap-am-cho-da-dau-pho-bien-cho\"><\/span><b>Top c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn cho\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u, n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u (oil-free) v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 nh\u01b0 d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c lotion. Nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2901\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2901\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/cap-am-cho-da-dau\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-hoat-chat\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2901\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2901\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-hoat-chat.webp\" alt=\"Top c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn cho da d\u1ea7u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-hoat-chat.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-hoat-chat-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-hoat-chat-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-hoat-chat-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2901\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Top c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid \u2013 gi\u00fap b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c n\u1eb7ng hay b\u1ebft d\u00ednh tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide: Gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 se kh\u00edt l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Acid Salicylic: H\u00fat d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba, l\u00e0m th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dimethicone: Gi\u00fap da kh\u00f4 r\u00e1o, kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng nh\u1eddn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ea5t s\u00e9t (Kaolin, Bentonite): Ki\u1ec1m d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glycolic Acid: Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00edt t\u1eafc ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinol: Ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n sinh collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chi-tiet-ve-cach-hoat-dong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid: L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u00e2n t\u1eed gi\u1eef \u1ea9m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn l\u1ea7n kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh n\u00f3, nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u v\u00e0o da, mang l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m s\u00e2u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y n\u1eb7ng m\u1eb7t hay l\u00e0m t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ecf, r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Acid Salicylic ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 \u2014 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dimethicone t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng tr\u00ean da, v\u1eeba d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u1eeba h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00f3ng d\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinol h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp da m\u1edbi, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc cho l\u00e0n da tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1, kh\u1ecfe kho\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y trong chu tr\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-cap-am-cho-da-dau-dung-cach\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n trong tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, h\u00e3y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da d\u1ea7u theo tr\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2902\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2902\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/cap-am-cho-da-dau\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-tot\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2902\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2902\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-tot.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m da d\u1ea7u \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-tot.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-tot-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-tot-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/cap-am-cho-da-dau-tot-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2902\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1ch c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m da d\u1ea7u \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ngay sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t: Khi da c\u00f2n \u1ea9m, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t s\u1ebd th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ch\u1ea5m l\u00ean c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed: tr\u00e1n, m\u0169i, c\u1eb1m v\u00e0 hai b\u00ean m\u00e1.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c massage nh\u1eb9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kem: Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kem b\u1eb1ng h\u1ea1t b\u1eafp, tr\u00e1nh b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng? C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00f3. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap da c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00f3ng nh\u1eddn, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1eady l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eddn r\u00edt, b\u00edt t\u1eafc? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay b\u00ed quy\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2903,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2900","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2900","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2900"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2900\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3986,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2900\/revisions\/3986"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2903"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2900"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2900"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2900"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}